@host = https://localhost:7060
@adminToken = <paste token from /auth/login response>
@userToken = <paste token from /auth/login response>

### Register a new user
POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login as admin (seeded automatically in Development)
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### Login as regular user
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Add a stock ticker (requires administrator role)
POST {{host}}/stocks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "ticker": "AAPL",
  "price": 189.45
}

###

### Get a stock price (requires any authenticated user)
GET {{host}}/stocks/AAPL
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###
